'''Yiggothal''' offered advice on the use of [[Snare rifle/Legends|Snare rifles]] in [[Gundark/Legends|Gundark's]] [[Gundark's Gear Datalog|Gear Datalog]] in [[6 ABY/Legends|41:6:1]]. Having seen the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Corwin Shelvay/Legends|Corwin Shelvay]] escape from a snare and kill the slaver pursuing him, Yiggothal was aware that while the weapon was effective in a surprise attack, it could be resisted if prepared for.

